snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 | Gameplay Trailer | Oculus Quest 2
snippet.description:
Play the survival-horror classic, Resident Evil 4 from an all-new first person perspective, now in VR for the first time. Blinking away won’t be an option. Available October 21, 2021.

Learn more at https://www.oculus.com/resident-evil-4
